<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Cascading Industries Q4 2024 Earnings Release</title>
    <style>
        * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }
        
        body {
            font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;
            background: #fff;
            color: #000;
            line-height: 1.5;
            padding: 0;
        }
        
        .header {
            background: #003366;
            color: #fff;
            padding: 30px 40px;
        }
        
        .header-content {
            max-width: 800px;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }
        
        .header h1 {
            font-family: 'Times New Roman', Times, serif;
            font-size: 24px;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        
        .ticker-info {
            font-size: 14px;
            opacity: 0.9;
        }
        
        .press-release {
            max-width: 800px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 40px;
        }
        
        .press-release > font[size="5"] {
            display: block;
            font-family: 'Times New Roman', Times, serif;
            font-size: 28px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            line-height: 1.3;
            color: #003366;
        }
        
        .press-release p {
            font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;
            font-size: 14px;
            text-align: justify;
            margin-bottom: 16px;
            text-indent: 0;
        }
        
        .press-release blockquote {
            margin: 24px 0;
            padding: 20px;
            border-left: 4px solid #003366;
            background: #f9f9f9;
        }
        
        .press-release blockquote font[size="2"] {
            display: block;
            font-family: 'Times New Roman', Times, serif;
            font-weight: bold;
            margin-bottom: 12px;
            color: #003366;
        }
        
        .press-release blockquote table {
            width: 100%;
            border-collapse: collapse;
            margin-top: 12px;
        }
        
        .press-release blockquote table td {
            padding: 8px 12px;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #ddd;
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            font-size: 13px;
        }
        
        .press-release blockquote table td:first-child {
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #333;
        }
        
        .press-release blockquote table td:last-child {
            text-align: right;
            font-family: 'Courier New', monospace;
        }
        
        .press-release font[size="3"] font[color="#000080"] {
            font-style: italic;
        }
        
        .press-release > font[size="2"] {
            display: block;
            margin-top: 30px;
            padding-top: 20px;
            border-top: 1px solid #ccc;
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #666666;
        }
        
        .disclaimer {
            font-size: 11px;
            color: #666;
            margin-top: 40px;
            text-align: left;
            font-style: italic;
            padding: 20px;
            background: #f5f5f5;
            border-left: 3px solid #003366;
        }
        
        .contact-info {
            margin-top: 20px;
            font-size: 12px;
            padding: 20px;
            background: #f9f9f9;
        }
        
        .press-release > font[size="3"]:last-of-type {
            display: block;
            background: #f0f0f0;
            padding: 16px;
            margin-top: 20px;
            border-left: 3px solid #003366;
        }
        
        .financial-highlights {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
            gap: 20px;
            margin: 30px 0;
        }
        
        .highlight {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 20px;
            background: #f9f9f9;
            border-radius: 8px;
        }
        
        .highlight-value {
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #003366;
        }
        
        .highlight-label {
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #666;
            margin-top: 5px;
        }
        
        .forward-looking {
            background: #fffbe6;
            border: 1px solid #ffe58f;
            padding: 15px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            font-size: 12px;
        }
        
        .forward-looking strong {
            color: #d48806;
        }
        
        .segments-table {
            margin: 30px 0;
        }
        
        .segments-table h3 {
            font-family: 'Times New Roman', Times, serif;
            font-size: 18px;
            color: #003366;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }
        
        .segments-table table {
            width: 100%;
            border-collapse: collapse;
        }
        
        .segments-table table td {
            padding: 10px 12px;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #ddd;
            font-size: 13px;
        }
        
        .segments-table table td:first-child {
            font-weight: bold;
        }
        
        .segments-table table td:last-child {
            text-align: right;
            font-family: 'Courier New', monospace;
        }
        
        .press-contact {
            margin-top: 30px;
            padding: 20px;
            background: #f0f5ff;
            border-radius: 8px;
        }
        
        .press-contact h4 {
            color: #003366;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        
        footer {
            background: #333;
            color: #fff;
            padding: 20px 40px;
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 11px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="header">
        <div class="header-content">
            <h1>CASCADING INDUSTRIES</h1>
            <div class="ticker-info">NYSE: CID | Press Release | FOR IMMEDIATE RELEASE</div>
        </div>
    </div>
    
    <div class="press-release">
        <font size="5" color="#003366"><b>Cascading Industries Reports Strong Q4 2024 Financial Results</b></font>
        
        <p><font size="3"><b>NEW YORK</b> - Cascading Industries (NYSE: CID) today announced financial results for the fourth quarter ended December 31, 2024, showing significant growth across all business segments with revenue increasing by 18% year-over-year and operating margins expanding to 24.3%.</font></p>
        
        <div class="financial-highlights">
            <div class="highlight">
                <div class="highlight-value">$4.2B</div>
                <div class="highlight-label">Revenue</div>
            </div>
            <div class="highlight">
                <div class="highlight-value">18%</div>
                <div class="highlight-label">YOY Growth</div>
            </div>
            <div class="highlight">
                <div class="highlight-value">24.3%</div>
                <div class="highlight-label">Operating Margin</div>
            </div>
            <div class="highlight">
                <div class="highlight-value">$3.42</div>
                <div class="highlight-label">EPS</div>
            </div>
        </div>
        
        <p><font size="3">The company's performance was driven by strong demand for its enterprise solutions portfolio, particularly in the cloud computing and artificial intelligence sectors where Cascading Industries has made substantial strategic investments over the past eighteen months.</font></p>
        
        <blockquote>
            <font size="2">Financial Summary (in millions USD):</font>
            <table border="1">
                <tr>
                    <td>Revenue</td>
                    <td>$4,230</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td>Operating Income</td>
                    <td>$1,028</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td>Net Income</td>
                    <td>$787</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td>EPS</td>
                    <td>$3.42</td>
                </tr>
            </table>
        </blockquote>
        
        <div class="segments-table">
            <h3>Revenue by Segment (Q4 2024)</h3>
            <table>
                <tr>
                    <td>Enterprise Solutions</td>
                    <td>$2,156M</td>
                    <td>+22%</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td>Cloud Services</td>
                    <td>$1,487M</td>
                    <td>+15%</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td>AI & Analytics</td>
                    <td>$587M</td>
                    <td>+31%</td>
                </tr>
            </table>
        </div>
        
        <p><font size="3">"We are pleased with our execution this quarter," said <font color="#000080"><i>CEO Margaret Chen</i></font>. "Our team has delivered outstanding results while simultaneously investing in next-generation technologies that will drive long-term growth. The AI sector particularly exceeded our expectations with 31% growth."</font></p>
        
        <p><font size="3">The company also announced that its board of directors has authorized a new share repurchase program of up to $2 billion, demonstrating confidence in the company's outlook and commitment to returning value to shareholders.</font></p>
        
        <div class="forward-looking">
            <strong>Forward-Looking Statements:</strong> This press release contains forward-looking statements within the meaning of Section 27A of the Securities Act of 1933. Actual results may differ materially from those projected. More information about factors that could affect the company's results is available in our SEC filings.
        </div>
        
        <p><font size="3">Looking ahead to 2025, the company expects continued momentum with revenue guidance of $4.8 to $5.1 billion, reflecting confidence in its product pipeline and market position. The company also raised its full-year 2025 operating margin guidance to 25%.</font></p>
        
        <div class="press-contact">
            <h4>Investor Relations Contact:</h4>
            <p>Jennifer Williams | VP Investor Relations</p>
            <p>investors@cascading.example.com | (212) 555-0100</p>
        </div>
        
        <font size="2" color="#666666">About Cascading Industries: Leading provider of enterprise software solutions serving Fortune 500 clients worldwide. Founded in 1998, the company operates in over 40 countries with more than 25,000 employees.</font>
        
        <div class="disclaimer">
            <strong>Safe Harbor Statement:</strong> This announcement contains forward-looking statements that involve risks and uncertainties. Detailed information about the company is contained in the reports filed with the Securities and Exchange Commission. Cascading Industries undertakes no obligation to update publicly any forward-looking statements.
        </div>
    </div>
    
    <footer>
        <p>&copy; 2024 Cascading Industries. All Rights Reserved.</p>
        <p>SEC Filing | Investor Relations | Press Releases | Corporate Governance</p>
    </footer>
</body>
</html>
